      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.hIhgdXnqGHBm0A64]{Envoy Improvisation}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;@Icon[type:language-dependent] Language-dependent @Icon[type:mind-affecting] Mind-Affecting @Icon[type:sense-dependent] Sense-Dependent</p>\n<p>As a move action, you can select an ally within 60 feet. Until the start of your next turn, that ally gains one of the following benefits: he can treat the armor check penalty of his armor as 4 lower than normal (to a minimum of 0); he can ignore the penalties for using armor or a weapon he is not proficient with; or he can ignore the broken condition of an item he is wearing or using.</p>"
